+ *   - Normalizes mtime on every file (including symlinks via `lutimes`).
+ *   - Tar with `--format=gnu --sort=name --owner=0 --group=0 --numeric-owner --mtime=@0 --no-acls --no-xattrs --no-selinux` + `gzip -n -9`.
